(a) If a Downgrade Event shall occur with respect to (i) any Downgraded Bank or (ii) any other Bank and, as a result thereof, such other Bank becomes a Downgraded Bank, then the Administrative Agent may, by notice to such Downgraded Bank and the Parent within 45 days after such Downgrade Event (any such notice, a ""), request that the Account Parties use reasonable efforts to replace such Bank as a party to this Agreement pursuant to . If such Bank is not so replaced within 45 days after receipt by the Account Parties of such Downgrade Notice, (x) if no Default exists and such Downgraded Bank has not exercised its right to remain a Bank hereunder pursuant to clause (y) below, the following shall occur concurrently:
