Item 8.01 Other Events.
 
On September 12, 2005, ACE Limited issued a press release with comments on the impact of Hurricane Katrina. The press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and is hereby incorporated herein by reference.
 
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits.
 
 
 
