day of April, 2006, before me personally came Robert Cusumano, to me known, who, being by me duly sworn, did depose and say that he is the General Counsel of ACE Limited, the corporation described in and which executed the above instrument; and that he signed his name thereto by order of the board of directors of said corporation.
 
 
