Consolidated Statement of Comprehensive Income
 
 
 
 
 
Income excluding net realized gains (losses) less perpetual preferred securities divided by average common shareholders' equity for the period. To annualize a quarterly rate multiply by four.
Annualized return on ordinary shareholders' equity (ROE):
 
Common shareholders' equity divided by the shares outstanding.
