On May 4, 2011, ACE Limited issued a press release reporting its first quarter 2011 results and the availability of its first quarter 2011 financial supplement. The press release and the financial supplement are attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and Exhibit 99.2, respectively, and are hereby incorporated herein by reference.
 
 
 
 
